# Git
.git
.gitignore

# Node
**/node_modules
**/.npm

# Build outputs (builder stage will create fresh ones)
**/dist
**/build

# Dev / test files
**/*.test.ts
**/*.spec.ts
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output

# Editor / OS
.vscode
.idea
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Secrets — never bake into images
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/main.parameters.json

# CI
.github

# Docs
**/*.md
